item.title: Pirelli returns to nudity with ‘sexy classic’ calendar for post-#MeToo era
item.description:
Ethan James Green says photos featuring semi-naked John Boyega and Padma Lakshmi are ‘about collaboration’

The photographer behind the next Pirelli calendar has vowed to make it sexy again after #MeToo “forced everyone to take a pause” and the company began capturing a fully-clothed cast.

John Boyega is among the celebrities posing for the 2025 edition, named Refresh and Reveal, with the musclebound British actor flexing and crouching on a Florida Keys beach – while an assistant splashes him with water for full effect.
